# asdf toolchain for emisar — `asdf install` from the repo root provisions the dev
# environment for every toolchain, and this file is the single source of truth
# for the Erlang + Elixir pins: the combined CI workflow reads it via setup-beam (version-file
# + version-type: strict), and the portal Docker build derives its --build-arg
# toolchain from it — so CI and the release image always match dev, nothing to
# hand-sync. golang: go.work + every go.mod and local development share the
# current security patch because CI and release builds use go-version-file.
# Go has no asdf plugin by default — run `asdf plugin add golang` once, then install.
